Partners





This company, based in Southwestern Ontario, has more than 50 years of design and system controls expertise. Their goal is to partner with industry to provide tailored solutions to engineering projects of all sizes. Whether they’re retrofitting an existing industrial plant, manufacturing line or production suite, or designing and developing automation controls from the ground up, their solutions include performance-focused design, end-to-end reliability and best-in-class safety control systems.
They have an extensive portfolio of experience within the industry in Canada and have also implemented large projects internationally in the United States, Panama, Colombia, China, and Ethiopia.



 
 



 






































































































































